## Multiple Date Formats in Same Document

- **Short format:** {{ Date.format(Date.buildTime(), "DD/MM/YYYY") }}
- **Full datetime:** {{ Date.format(Date.buildTime(), "YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss") }}
- **Compact:** {{ Date.format(Date.buildTime(), "YYYYMMDD") }}

## Combining with Other Functions

### With String Functions

Compact date: {{ String.replace(Date.format(Date.buildTime(), "YYYY-MM-DD"), "-", "") }}

### With Math Functions

- Timestamp in milliseconds: {{ Date.msTimestamp(Date.buildTime()) }}
- Timestamp in seconds: {{ Date.timestamp(Date.buildTime()) }}
- Timestamp in minutes: {{ Math.round(Date.timestamp(Date.buildTime()) / 60) }}

### In Conditional Blocks

:::if {{ Date.timestamp(Date.buildTime()) > Date.timestamp(Date.buildTime()) }}
**This document has been updated since creation.**

Last update: {{ Date.format(Date.buildTime(), "DD/MM/YYYY HH:mm") }}
:::

