## Date.buildTime() Function
$lang = $backLang
Get the current date and time:
- **Current date:** {{ Date.format(Date.buildTime(), "DD/MM/YYYY") }}
- **Current datetime:** {{ Date.format(Date.buildTime(), "YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss") }}

