## Best Practices

### Consistent Formatting

Define a variable for repeated formats:

$fmt = "DD/MM/YYYY"

Created: {{ Date.format(Date.buildTime(), $fmt) }}

Modified: {{ Date.format(Date.buildTime(), $fmt) }}

### Always Show Both Dates

**Created:** {{ Date.format(Date.buildTime(), "DD MMMM YYYY") }}

**Last modified:** {{ Date.format(Date.buildTime(), "DD MMMM YYYY 'at' HH:mm") }}

